      <arrangement id="aspace_3bb90b808f368ff6ff1f5ad13a62ecfe">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Organized into two series: I. Writings by Chauncey Pratt Williams, 1916-1934. II. Writings by Others, 1920-1953.</p>  
      </arrangement>
